    <string name="welcome_text" formatted="false">Recording conversations without consent
        is illegal in many states. Do the right thing: get consent before using BlabberTabber.\n
        \nBlabberTabber records conversations and calculates how much each
        person spoke.  It is under construction.  It does not work yet.\n
        \nTo pause, press "PAUSE", to resume, press
        "RECORD", and to reset the tally, press "RESET".\n
        \nWhen the meeting is over, press "FINISH" to see the final tally.\n
    </string>
